Five winners. Five projects. Five dreams. 💙

Since winning the Blue Creator Fund, Ebele, Gabin, Letitia, Still Shadey and Jerrell have been on a creative journey of a lifetime with funding from @ChelseaFCFoundation and mentoring from @Nicholas_Daley.

Come and see their final work as part of This Game Is What We Make It, Chelsea’s exhibition celebrating 120 years this weekend only at @SaatchiGallery.
